repos/marcorieser/statamic-livewire","labels_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/marcorieser/statamic-livewire/issues/26/labels{/name}","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/marcorieser/statamic-livewire/issues/26/comments","events_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/marcorieser/statamic-livewire/issues/26/events","html_url":"https://github.com/marcorieser/statamic-livewire/issues/26","id":4273183076,"node_id":"I_kwDONtGGfs7-s5lk","number":26,"title":"HydrateCascadeByLivewireUrl crashes on Route::statamic() routes (null content)","user":{"login":"jonathan-bird","id":1510001,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjE1MTAwMDE=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1510001?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/jonathan-bird","html_url":"https://github.com/jonathan-bird","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jonathan-bird/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jonathan-bird/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jonathan-bird/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jonathan-bird/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jonathan-bird/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jonathan-bird/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jonathan-bird/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jonathan-bird/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jonathan-bird/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"labels":[],"state":"closed","locked":false,"assignees":[],"milestone":null,"comments":6,"created_at":"2026-04-16T04:08:05Z","updated_at":"2026-04-16T06:09:58Z","closed_at":"2026-04-16T05:29:50Z","assignee":null,"author_association":"NONE","active_lock_reason":null,"sub_issues_summary":{"total":0,"completed":0,"percent_completed":0},"issue_dependencies_summary":{"blocked_by":0,"total_blocked_by":0,"blocking":0,"total_blocking":0},"body":"## Bug\n\nWhen a Livewire component is embedded in a page served by `Route::statamic()`, any Livewire update request (e.g. pagination) throws:\n\n```\nCall to a member function toArray() on null\nvendor/statamic/cms/src/View/Cascade.php:167\n```\n\n## What's happening\n\n`HydrateCascadeByLivewireUrl::hydrateContent()` does this:\n\n```php\nCascade::withContent(fn () => Data::findByRequestUrl(Livewire::originalUrl()));\n```\n\nFor `Route::statamic()` routes there's no content entry, so `Data::findByRequestUrl()` returns `null`. But because it's wrapped in a closure, the Cascade's null guard at the top of `hydrateContent()` doesn't catch it -- a `Closure` is truthy. After the closure resolves to `null`, the code continues and calls `->toArray()` on it.\n\nOn the initial page load this isn't a problem because `FrontendController::route()` passes `null` directly (not wrapped in a closure), so the Cascade's `if (! $this->content) { return $this; }` check works fine.\n\n## How to reproduce\n\n1. Define a custom route:\n\n```php\n// routes/web.php\nRoute::statamic('events', 'events.index', [\n    'seo_enabled' => true,\n    'seo_title' => 'Events',\n]);\n```\n\n2. Create a Livewire component with pagination (or any action that triggers an update request) and embed it in the `events.index` view.\n\n3. Load the page -- works fine.\n\n4. Trigger a Livewire update (click to page 2, apply a filter, etc.) -- 500 error.\n\nHaving `aerni/advanced-seo` installed makes it more likely to hit this because its `CascadeComposer` calls `$cascade->hydrate()` during view composition, but the underlying bug is in the middleware regardless.\n\n## Suggested fix\n\nResolve the content before passing it to the Cascade, and skip it when null:\n\n```php\nprotected function hydrateContent(): void\n{\n    $content = Data::findByRequestUrl(Livewire::originalUrl());\n\n    if ($content) {\n        Cascade::withContent($content);\n    }\n}\n```\n\n## Environment\n\n- statamic-livewire: v5.3.0\n- statamic/cms: v6.13.0\n- aerni/advanced-seo: v2.14.1\n- livewire/livewire: v3\n- PHP: 8.3","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/marcorieser/statamic-livewire/issues/26/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"timeline_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/marcorieser/statamic-livewire/issues/26/timeline","performed_via_github_app":null,"state_reason":"completed","pinned_comment":null,"score":1.0},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/duncanmcclean/statamic-cargo/issues/161","repository_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/duncanmcclean/statamic-cargo","labels_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/duncanmcclean/statamic-cargo/issues/161/labels{/name}","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/duncanmcclean/statamic-cargo/issues/161/comments","events_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/duncanmcclean/statamic-cargo/issues/161/events","html_url":"https://github.com/duncanmcclean/statamic-cargo/issues/161","id":4204556178,"node_id":"I_kwDOOIsPe876nG-S","number":161,"title":"Error adding product","user":{"login":"benya","id":2229023,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjIyMjkwMjM=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/2229023?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/benya","html_url":"https://github.com/benya","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/benya/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/benya/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/benya/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/benya/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/benya/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/benya/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/benya/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/benya/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/benya/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"labels":[{"id":8294861570,"node_id":"LA_kw