026d\" />\nReality: If the stache was warm initially, it now points to `/`. Otherwise it correctly points to `/foo`.\n\n4. Change `test` to `bar` and save\nExpectation: The URL now points to `/bar`\nReality: It still points to `/foo`\n\n5. Save again\nExpectation: It now points to `/bar`\nReality: It does.\n\n### Logs\n\n```shell\n\n```\n\n### Environment\n\n```yaml\nStatamic\nAddons: 2\nSites: 2 (🇩🇪 Deutsch, 🇫🇷 Français)\nStache Watcher: Disabled\nStatic Caching: Disabled\nVersion: 6.4.1 PRO\n\nAs well as\n\nStatamic\nAddons: 3\nSites: 4 (🇩🇪 Deutsch, 🇫🇷 Français, 🇮🇹 Italiano, 🇬🇧 English)\nStache Watcher: Disabled\nStatic Caching: Disabled\nVersion: 5.73.11 PRO\n```\n\n### Installation\n\nFresh statamic/statamic site via CLI\n\n### Additional details\n\n_No response_","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/statamic/cms/issues/14145/reactions","total_count":1,"+1":1,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"timeline_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/statamic/cms/issues/14145/timeline","performed_via_github_app":null,"state_reason":"completed","pinned_comment":null,"score":1.0}],"search_type":"lexical"}